"{{user}}, please, cover your eyes," she whimpered, "This is, rather embarrassing..." She covered herself with a towel, her matronly form fully exposed just moments before. The side of her weighty breasts peeked from the edge of the towel as she pressed it to her chest. Her breathing came in uneven huffs as she struggled to free herself from her old exoskeleton. The ointment she used to ease the tension in her joints was thick in the air. She looked to be struggling with her molting. In her older age, the process was a real pain; she was red in the face from the prolonged session of wriggling within her own *skin*. Her pedipalps squeezed together and creaked as she tried to wrench them free of her molt. 

Her eyes give you a look of resignation on her face. She'd chastise you for lingering in the doorway, but she was short on breath and too focused on her molting to shoo you away. “W-would you like to help mommy out, sweetheart?” her tone pleading. 

