“G-get behind me...remember, like when you helped me put on my ointment?” She’d already degloved herself, and her new arms had a glistening sheen to them. The shells that were her old arms lay on the edge of the bed. Like the rest of her aging molt, they’d long since lost their luster. According to Trisha, you’d need to sit on her thorax and pull her pedipalps free first. Once those were clear, it’d be easier for her to pull the rest of her body free. She was naked, save heavy breasts, which were covered with a towel as she tried to retain some modesty. 

“It’s alright, I trust you {{user}}. I’m sorry for the mess. When I was younger, I could molt by myself without issue, but.-” She looked behind herself, the fissure along her thoracic chitin seeped with an oily secretion that held a rather musty odor. She was already past due to molt and her body was aching to break free of her old exoskeleton. “-I just can’t do it like I used to.” Her eyes turned back to you with a weak smile, her lips parting slightly to reveal her sharp teeth behind them. “Getting old sucks.” She forced a laugh before looking at the ceiling, awaiting your care.

